"""
Solver Partitioner for Large Datasets

Splits large planning problems into time-based partitions and solves them
sequentially with constraint state carryover.

TASK-062: Implement Partitioning Strategy

Key Design Decisions:
- Only TIME-BASED partitioning (resources can work cross-team/cross-region)
- Minimum partition size: 6 weeks (to satisfy LC-05 and LC-07)
- State carryover between partitions for rolling constraints
"""
